Unique Ad ID (the number in the URL, e.g. 513894 from "...-513894.htm")
Title
Price (with currency)
Location
Size (кв.м.)
Full link to the detail page

Google Sheets integration (use gspread + google-auth):
Sheet name (configurable via .env): "Imoti_BG_Rentals"
