Logic for "new" ads and classification:
Load all existing Ad_ID from "Processed_IDs" into a set.
For every scraped ad:
If Ad_ID already in Processed_IDs → skip.
If new → go to the detail page.
On the detail page extract the phone number (it is a clickable  link, usually under "### Частно лице" or agency name).
Normalize phone (remove all non-digits, keep only Bulgarian format, e.g. 0894860795).
Check if this normalized phone exists in the "Agencies" sheet.
If yes → Type = "від агенції"
If no → Type = "приватний"

